room_title: Escape room "The Godfather's Secret" by Escape! Spokane in Spokane
review: Four of us attempted Godfathers Secret escape room this week at E 12928 Indiana location. Luke, our host, was very pleasant and entertaining. It definitely was challenging and fun looking for clues. No, we didn't make it out in the 60 minutes, but we enjoyed our time trying to make our escape.

room_title: Escape room "The Godfather's Secret" by Escape! Spokane in Spokane
review: We did The Godfather room in Spokane Valley. The puzzles were great and even though we didn't get out we had a blast! We took 4 people including 2 kids who loved it.

room_title: Escape room "The Godfather's Secret" by Escape! Spokane in Spokane
review: We did The Godfather theme in Spokane Valley. It was a blast! Brad was a great host! Thanks for the fun!
